{"TopicId":203182,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"How to move the NavBall","CreatedByName":"MetricKerbalist","CreatedById":211699,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-06-21T21:56:42Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"MetricKerbalist","CreatedById":211699,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-06-21T21:56:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHi KSP colleagues,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI was watching a video where the NavBall was off to the side of the screen.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat interested me, because I find that the NavBall placed in the center is often in the way.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHowever, I cannot figure out how to move it.\u00A0 Could one of you nice people please tell me how to do it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThank you for your consideration.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nStanley\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Echo__3","CreatedById":204997,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-06-21T22:19:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI use the mod\u00A0Draggable Navball to move it around. It can drag it with the curser left or right as needed.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"18Watt","CreatedById":198538,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-06-21T22:29:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs there a way to do this in the stock game?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MetricKerbalist","CreatedById":211699,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-06-21T23:41:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223992695\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022203182\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221624314544\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022198538\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u002218Watt\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, 18Watt said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs there a way to do this in the stock game?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRight.\u00A0 That was going to be my next question.\u00A0 Thank you, \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/198538-18watt/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022198538\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/198538-18watt/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@18Watt\u003C/a\u003E, for your asking it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd thank you, \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/204997-echo__3/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022204997\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/204997-echo__3/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Echo__3\u003C/a\u003E, for answering my first question.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Superfluous J","CreatedById":73725,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-06-22T00:04:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn the stock game, it\u0027s in settings. Hit ESC choose settings (options? I don\u0027t recall) and it\u0027s somewhere in those menus.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSadly I can\u0027t start the game right now to check.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Anth","CreatedById":161238,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-06-22T00:26:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBe in scene (looking at your craft in the world) then\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Col\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nPress Escape\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nClick on settings\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nScroll down to the bottom of the settings and you will see NavBall Pos (Left\u0026lt;-\u0026gt;Right)\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nMove slider right or left\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ol\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022fLaRpq8.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002290.00\u0022 height=\u0022675\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/fLaRpq8.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\nApply, Accept, Close\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MetricKerbalist","CreatedById":211699,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-06-22T00:38:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223992740\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022203182\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221624321601\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022161238\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Anth12\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n11 minutes ago, Anth12 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBe in scene (looking at your craft in the world) then\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Col\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nPress Escape\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nClick on settings\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nScroll down to the bottom of the settings and you will see NavBall Pos (Left\u0026lt;-\u0026gt;Right)\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nMove slider right or left\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ol\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\nApply, Accept, Close\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat did it, \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/161238-anth12/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022161238\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/161238-anth12/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Anth12\u003C/a\u003E.\u00A0 Great.\u00A0 thank you.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222021-06-22T00:39:31Z\u0022 title=\u002206/22/2021 12:39  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EJune 22, 2021\u003C/time\u003E by MetricKerbalist\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Anth","CreatedById":161238,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-06-22T00:42:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou are welcome\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}